longBusinessSummary: Westwing Group AG, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the home and living ecommerce business. The company operates through two segments, DACH and International. It offers textile products, rugs, home dÃ©cor and accessories, kitchen and dining products, lighting products, furniture products, and other products. The company provides its products under own and private label, and third-party brands. It has operations in 11 European countries, including Germany, Switzerland, Austria, Spain, Italy, France, Poland, the Czech Republic, Slovakia, Belgium, and the Netherlands. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany.
